.TH FLOPPY 3 
.SH NAME
floppy \- floppy disk interface
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B bind #f /dev

.B /dev/fd0disk
.B /dev/fd1disk
.B /dev/fd2disk
.B /dev/fd3disk
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
The floppy disk interface serves a one-level directory giving access to up
to four floppy disk drives.
Each drive is represented as a single file.
There are no partitions.
